理',NULL),(14,'2014-10-29 11:13:53','8510122',NULL,'<p><span style=\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 20px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 24px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;自主创业奖励</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\">1.一寸照片2张</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\">2.身份证复印件（正反面）</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\">3.户口复印件（首页、户主页和本人页）</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\">4.就业失业登记证</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\">5.营业执照正本复印件（2009年后办理的，缩印成A4）</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\">6.按营业执照时间 签订的一年以上租赁协议及租赁收据或发票复印件（租赁收据或发票上要注明出租人的联系电话及租赁地址）</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\">7.和一名员工签订的一年以上劳动合同及给该名员工缴纳社保的凭证复印件(社保凭证要在营业执照时间之后缴费记录要近半年以上的)</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\">8.创业奖励及场租申请表</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\">9.经营场所门头照片（电子档和纸质）</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\">10、SYB（创业）培训合格证书原件及复印件</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16px;\">11、以上资料一式三份</span></p><p><br/></p><p></p>',' 自主创业奖励',NULL),(16,'2014-10-29 11:13:51','8510122',NULL,'<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 24px;\">就业困难人员认定工作流程</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-left: 48px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">1、<span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">贵阳市就业困难人员认定申请表</span>2<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">份</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-left: 48px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">2、<span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">身份证复印件